The paper discusses deep learning toolkits and libraries for intelligent user interfaces, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The paper also mentions natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG) as relevant areas for deep learning in IUI. Finally, the paper is focused on the practical implementation of deep learning techniques, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
